

Problems Encountered While Building OUI
    
* the lower layer (done)
* building out UI tree (stole DOM) (done)
* layout (vbox/hbox simplified flex)
* scroll view (regions) (Flutter's layout)
* flickering (double buffering)
* events / event loop
* good representation of styled string (sstring)
* how to handle dirty checking / dirty tracking? (Don't)
* keyboard focus / text fields
* double-clicks
* window system
    * window overlapping
    * drag/resize
* trees
* absolute position
* event bubbling
